B.O.A.T.S. II: Me Time is the second studio album by American rapper 2 Chainz, a sequel to his gold certified, Grammy-nominated debut album Based on a T.R.U. Story. The album was released in the United States through Def Jam Recordings, on September 10, 2013. The album features guest appearances from Pharrell Williams, Fergie, Drake, Lil Wayne, Pusha T, Mase, Chrisette Michele, Iamsu!, T-Pain, Dolla Boy, Rich Homie Quan, and Lloyd among others. The album's production was handled by Diplo, Mike WiLL Made It, Drumma Boy, J.U.S.T.I.C.E. League, Mannie Fresh, Wonder Arillo, Da Honorable C-Note and DJ Toomp among others. It was supported by the lead single "Feds Watching" featuring Pharrell Williams.
